metadata.name: Gae Catto
metadata.description:
A black catto and his flowery kimono. This extra catto is a self-proclaimed diva and a drag queen who only dreams of becoming....

In the middle of a photoshoot, he is distracted - “What do I eat next? Do I look good in this kimono? AM I PULLING THIS OFF?”

2000x2000pixels, 30 frames 

The owner of this piece will receive an airdrop(through Opensea) a loop animation of a cat holding a flower.
1280x1280pixels
